Notebook[{
Cell["\<\
The aim is to train a classifier to distinguish the temperature in Aberdeen, \
Auckland and Jeddah using data from  January, 2020 to December, 2023. 

To do that, use the WeatherData function to obtain the time series for the \
mean daily temperature in Aberdeen, Auckland and Jeddah from  January, 2020 \
to December, 2023. 

Split the data into a training and testing dataset as follows: The training \
dataset consists of 200 randomly chosen temperature values from each city; \
the rest of values from each city define the testing dataset. 

Train a classifier using the training data and study its performance using \
the ROC curves for the test data. Comment on the results.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.906181893850789*^9, 3.9061823494773083`*^9}, {
  3.953868148681534*^9, 3.9538682943426495`*^9}, {3.9538683368698425`*^9, 
  3.953868356618263*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d38cb6fc-d984-4cd2-84d8-\
343d159f9475"],

